-------------------------------------------------------------
      PROJECT OPEN SKY AIRCRAFT ARCHIVE FOR FS9 AND FSX
-------------------------------------------------------------

This is complete archive of Project Open Sky (POSKY) before their website went down for good. (Archive contains 889 files for a total of 8.22GB.)

Files consist of all of the Model, FDE, Paint Kits, Liveries, Sound and Panel packages that were available as of 18 December 2014.
